BTG Pactual to Purchase Banco Panamericano’s Shares Outstanding

-- B y   S t e p h a n   N i e l s e n
-- 
2011-05-28T15:45:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-28/btg-pactual-to-purchase-banco-panamericano-s-shares-outstanding.html
Banco BTG Pactual SA, the Brazilian
investment bank controlled by billionaire  Andre Esteves , plans
to buy the non-voting shares outstanding of  Banco Panamericano
SA. (BPNM4)   BTG didn’t provide financial details or say when it plans
to carry out the purchase, according to a regulatory filing
yesterday.  The bank has acquired a controlling stake in the Sao Paulo-
based lender, according to the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stephan Nielsen in Sao Paulo at 
 snielsen8@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Will Wade at 
 wwade4@bloomberg.net . 